{"tid":886640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB台慶劇係大陸全面仆直, 仲輸埋比敵對港劇","createTime":"2018-11-02T08:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T10:41:19.000Z","uid":134071,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"727e47696ea5dfe40a90d8df3cb954267b214f97","tid":886640,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T08:57:27.000Z","msg":"CCTVB要專攻大陸,  但《跳躍生命線》同《是咁的，法官閣下》係大陸網站都仆直, 仲衰過黃viu外購港劇....<br />\n<br />\n《跳躍生命線》大陸點擊率有8878萬, 而播左四集既《是咁的，法官閣下》在優酷有1947萬點擊率, 以大陸標準上係仆直.<br />\n<a href=\"http://list.youku.com/show/id_z895be11272b442c98c16.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flist.youku.com%2Fshow%2Fid_z895be11272b442c98c16.html&d=QEVk%2FwPgkJ%2FS4306LLtS%2FcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0f2a0a69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://list.youku.com/show/id_z895be11272b442c98c16.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://list.youku.com/show/id_z3b5e2c2736e5486b86f6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flist.youku.com%2Fshow%2Fid_z3b5e2c2736e5486b86f6.html&d=QEVk%2FwPgkJ%2FS4306LLtS%2FcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f6467c26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://list.youku.com/show/id_z3b5e2c2736e5486b86f6.html</a><br />\n<br />\n反而, 香港黃viu外購既中港合拍劇《蝕日風暴》於大陸網絡開播不足一星期, 點擊率已經突破1億.  而家, 《蝕日風暴》大陸點擊率已經突破17億 .<br />\n<a href=\"http://list.youku.com/show/id_z4d722befbfbdefbfbd1d.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flist.youku.com%2Fshow%2Fid_z4d722befbfbdefbfbd1d.html&d=QEVk%2FwPgkJ%2FS4306LLtS%2FcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f9ab6820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://list.youku.com/show/id_z4d722befbfbdefbfbd1d.html</a><br />\n<br />\n(上年套《反黑》, 亦係於大陸網絡開播不足一星期, 點擊率已經突破1億....)"},{"pid":"cd87158d2efff02e44717ea0241f968d5d5fa68c","tid":886640,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"早排youku有時會飛套蝕日風暴既廣告出黎"},{"pid":"2c720c6550cb6929aa836a01aab0d926c4c61fc1","tid":886640,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB